{"tid":2062181,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥關注事件一週年關注區！！！","createTime":"2020-06-13T03:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T05:53:47.000Z","uid":73381,"like":27,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a168a2ab3d085ab79224b8512d5b3db60487cf2b","tid":2062181,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"一年了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n達哥，你最近還好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n很想跟你講一句，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WeEnxMP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWeEnxMP.png&h=4c3e1bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WaOqgbw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWaOqgbw.png&h=23e05550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n六四一開台 你卻為銀紙<br />\nblock鳩巴打你怕受罪<br />\n完全忘記往日為何<br />\n凌晨仍朝共潑水<br />\n<br />\n難道我我我我我對達哥已死心<br />\n貪得意好心敷衍一下卻逼真的悲憫<br />\n達朝已滅亡太開心<br />\n分不出警犬的愛恨<br />\n<br />\n無謂汪汪汪汪汪太過做作不堪<br />\n我估錯這個撚樣得到教訓<br />\n怎相信人 還該怎麼吊柒你為人<br />\n<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrgu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=ef6a123d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n<br />\n我都唔知點解我忽然對你無晒感覺<br />\n以前嗰種快樂就好似成為一種罪惡<br />\n連你開台 我都唔多覺<br />\n或者其實所謂關注都只係希望搵個寄托<br />\n或者係贊成修例嘅悟覺<br />\n連自己都唔知道 乜係禮 乜嘢係樂<br />\n幾時奶中國 又幾時無埋思覺<br />\n就算你條撚樣失去下落<br />\n完美世界都可能已經落幕"},{"pid":"645a622d4ab201b00ea86ed2a0b9c35a8b537704","tid":2062181,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T03:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d730df6dd3460875c91f